{"TopicId":186953,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Scale setting problem","CreatedByName":"P Express Space \u0026amp; Sky Dept","CreatedById":199223,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-04T18:30:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"P Express Space \u0026amp; Sky Dept","CreatedById":199223,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-04T18:30:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know this maybe a stupid question but i still need to ask...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see many ppl in yt and forums that they can set the scale of wings, ailerons or sth kinda like that, but how can they open the \u0022window\u0022 to set the scale?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMods? Add-ons?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-04T19:49:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a mod called Tweakscale.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"P Express Space \u0026amp; Sky Dept","CreatedById":199223,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-05T16:08:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223645717\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186953\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564948187\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a mod called Tweakscale.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat means I need to download mods?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-05T18:30:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you feel that you are simply unable to build the craft that you want while using stock-sized parts, then yes, downloading that one mod is one\u00A0other route to go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlternately, there are other mods that provide parts that may already be exactly what you want, without providing the \u0022scaling\u0022 feature that you asked about.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut deciding to stick with only stock parts places some limits on what you can get away with constructing. On the other hand, getting around those limits, and building what you want in spite of the limits, is another form of creativity that the game encourages. If you can manage to do it, because that obviously makes it a lot harder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-05T18:31:26Z\u0022 title=\u002208/05/2019 06:31  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 5, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by bewing\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-05T19:15:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoving to Add-on Discussions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"P Express Space \u0026amp; Sky Dept","CreatedById":199223,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-10T18:36:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx I found the add-on and using that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-17T16:50:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223648585\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186953\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221565462160\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199223\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022P Express Space \u0026amp; Sky Dept\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/10/2019 at 3:36 PM, P Express Space \u0026amp; Sky Dept said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx I found the add-on and using that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi! There\u0027s another Add\u0027On (or \u0022Mod\u0022) that I recommend to use. \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94997-171-save-automatic-backup-system-155-3121/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ES.A.V.E.\u003C/a\u003E. It\u0027s for automatic backups of your savegames.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow and then some interactions between different Add\u0027Ons can cause misbehaviours on the game . Using a backup Add\u0027On will make sure the misbehavior will be a nuisance, and not a trouble.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-17T16:51:24Z\u0022 title=\u002208/17/2019 04:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 17, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Lisias\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EHit \u0026quot;Save\u0026quot; too soon.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}